    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "おらー、ポンコツマネージャー！\nもっと気合いを入れろー！！",
      "startTime": 6.8333331684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そんないきなり、水しぶきを撮影したいから\nプールに波を立てろと言われても",
      "startTime": 12.2666666288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ビート板とか、掃除用のモップも借りてきましたし\nこれでも精一杯やってるんですがっ……",
      "startTime": 18.4999999622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなチャプチャプした波、いくら立てたって\n全然、迫力が出ないじゃん！",
      "startTime": 24.0000005979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "もっと全身を使って！\nそうだ、いっそあんたがプールに飛び込めばいいんだ！",
      "startTime": 29.600002251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無茶言わないで下さい\n俺、水着持ってきてないですし、着替えもっ……",
      "startTime": 35.9666676461,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pillow-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6999.999147700002,
          "startTime": 42.9666667938
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "うるさい、マネージャーなら体を張れ！！\nおりゃーっ！！",
      "startTime": 42.7333343128,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9991098000037,
          "startTime": 43.9333334226
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9991098000037,
          "startTime": 43.9333334226
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9991098000037,
          "startTime": 43.9333334226
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "よっしゃ、よくやった！\n水しぶきは……よしよし、いい感じに撮れてる",
      "startTime": 47.8666675189,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.340263299995,
          "startTime": 53.2000077822
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ほ、本当にプールに突き落とさないで下さいよ\nああ、なんでこんな目に……",
      "startTime": 60.9333342234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "なんでって、金がないんだからしょうがないでしょ",
      "startTime": 64.5333411155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "で、金がなくなったのはあんたのせいでもあるんだから\n文句言わずに、キリキリ働け！！",
      "startTime": 72.7333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一週間ほど前",
      "startTime": 76.9333334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1600.0000000000086,
          "startTime": 78.5333334605
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、kanaさん。ちょうど良かった\n密着取材でお疲れのところすみませんが、少し相談が",
      "startTime": 81.8333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "いやもう本当に疲れたわよ、あれ\n楽屋でもホテルでもカメラに追い回されるし",
      "startTime": 90.1333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "挙げ句、どっかの誰かがいきなり曲を作れとか言うし\nでも、ばしっと名曲作れるのがさすがkanaだよね",
      "startTime": 99.8666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "今回はkana、作詞家と作曲家の仕事と\nすぐボロ出しそうになるバカ二人の子守もしたんだし",
      "startTime": 108.9333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あんたの相談ってのも、その分のギャラとボーナスを\nkanaにくれるって、そういう話なんだよね？",
      "startTime": 116.7000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、franさんみたいなことおっしゃいますね……",
      "startTime": 121.5666830955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "いや、人として言っていいことと悪いことがあるでしょ\nあの銭ゲバと一緒にされるとか屈辱",
      "startTime": 129.9666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこまで言わなくても……\nそれと……残念ながら、ボーナスはちょっと難しいかと",
      "startTime": 137.2333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　なんでよ",
      "startTime": 141.8666790265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "franさんがデザインした新曲の衣装\nあれ高級素材をかなり使ってまして、制作費がもう……",
      "startTime": 147.2666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "あの衣装、いつもよりむしろ面積狭かったじゃん！\nそれをどうやったら衣装だけで予算削れる訳！？",
      "startTime": 156.7000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "franさんのこだわり……ですかね……\nそれと、ホテルのサービス料も結構掛かりまして",
      "startTime": 164.4666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "確かにfranのやつ、ホテルのエステに行ってたな\nルームサービスで北京ダックも頼んでたし",
      "startTime": 173.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "あとシャンパンとかワイン、ガブ飲みしてたっぽい\nあいつ無駄にフランス語読めるし、半端に知識あるから",
      "startTime": 180.6666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ事務所がまとめて払うんだしー、とか言って\n高いボトル頼みまくったんじゃないかな",
      "startTime": 188.3482182334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "だからあいつに月に五百円以上渡したら駄目だっての！",
      "startTime": 191.5333589176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "小学生のお小遣い以下ですね……",
      "startTime": 196.8333589176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ聞くけど、あれが中学生以上に見える？\n足し算引き算と小遣い帳のつけ方も怪しいけど？",
      "startTime": 204.533347702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやー……さすがにそこまでは……",
      "startTime": 209.3333599348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "って言うか、そんなに金がなくなってるなら\n新曲の宣伝とかMVはどうすんの？",
      "startTime": 217.5000143687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "あの辺の仕事はまだこれからだよね？\n宣伝なしで新曲出すとか、自殺行為じゃん！",
      "startTime": 224.133347702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、それで三枝さんと頭を抱えてまして……\nスリクスの皆さんにも相談しようと、探してたんです",
      "startTime": 232.0666810353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "うげ。社長に睨まれるとか、勘弁してよね",
      "startTime": 236.3667014062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan023.m4a",
      "text": "あんたがfranに好き放題させたのが悪いんだから\n責任取って、給料返上してこっちの宣伝に回せ！",
      "startTime": 244.6333466847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan024.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、駄目か。あんたの月給じゃ\nせいぜい電車のつり革広告一本分にしかならないし",
      "startTime": 253.1000194549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ご理解いただけて助かります……",
      "startTime": 257.3666983544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan025.m4a",
      "text": "宣伝費はゼロに出来ないけど\nMVなら事務所で作れば、かなり経費削れるはず……",
      "startTime": 263.3666861216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan026.m4a",
      "text": "こうなったら、あんたがMVの監督やって！\nなんとかするのがマネージャーの仕事でしょ？",
      "startTime": 272.8333507537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "え、俺ですか！？",
      "startTime": 275.8333751936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan027.m4a",
      "text": "明日までに、MVのプラン考えて持ってくること",
      "startTime": 277.866708527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_01-kan028.m4a",
      "text": "使えねープラン持ってきたら\n本当に給料から予算を出してもらうからね！",
      "startTime": 284.6333507537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
